This plugin provides Zero Trust network segmentation and inter-zone access control for OPNsense,
enforcing strict policies between logical network zones based on explicit rules.

Key Features:
- Define custom zones (e.g., office, lab, guest) with associated subnets or IP ranges.
- Block all inter-zone communication by default (Zero Trust enforcement).
- Allow specific flows through granular, rule-based exceptions.
- Supports IT and OT environments, including industrial protocols (Modbus, DNP3, OPC UA).
- Modern web UI for creating zones and managing access rules.

